    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this thing since day one, keeping it spotless and always garaged. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
