    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, maintained in a strictly stock configuration. This example features the legendary 13B-REW rotary engine with its sequential twin-turbocharger system functioning flawlessly; the transition at 4,500 RPM is seamless, providing linear power delivery across the rev range. The longitudinal front-midship layout ensures a perfect 50:50 weight distribution, complemented by the original four-wheel aluminum double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis remains rigid with zero oxidation, and the vacuum manifold\u2014often a point of failure\u2014is in pristine, heat-shielded condition. This is a collector-quality specimen with a factory-spec five-speed manual transmission, offering the precise mechanical feedback and high-revving performance the FD chassis is renowned for.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
