    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to own a true 'time capsule' specimen. Maintained to a concours standard, the exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory finish with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, thanks to a professional ceramic coating and climate-controlled storage. The interior is equally impeccable; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear or creasing, the dashboard is flawless, and the cabin still retains its original factory scent. Mechanically, this car is indistinguishable from new. It has been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a full, documented history of preventative maintenance performed well ahead of manufacturer intervals. The engine bay is pristine, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting a life spent far away from harsh weather or salted roads. This sale includes all original keys, the factory window sticker, owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom-fit car cover. For the collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the definitive example you have been searching for.",
      "price": 46500.0,
